OL,5, One day in February 2020, Laura's      
OL,6, partner went out for a run and never   
OL,7, came back - leaving her to care for    
OL,8, their two-year-old son on her own.     
OL,10,F"We waited and waited, then went out to
OL,11,Ffind him," she recalls. After coming   
OL,12,Facross an ambulance, she was shocked to
OL,13,Fdiscover that he had died of a sudden  
OL,14,Fheart attack.                          
OL,16,FCompounding Laura's intense grief was  
OL,17,Fthe fact she was not able to claim     
OL,18,Fbereavement benefits as she had not    
OL,19,Fbeen married or in a civil partnership.
